I’ll be gone til November

Still on a high. For my 28th, these women came together & surprised me with the best gift I could ever ask for, and if you know me I hardly ever ask lol They poured into me. I was celebrated & surrounded with love. They traveled from all over, set up an amazing picnic, we laughed, we drank/ate, we sang, we twerked in the sunset, we cried, we enjoyed ourselves. I’ve never had friends like this & I feel truly blessed. As the only child, this sisterhood means more than you’ll know. I love each of you, & again thank you thank you thank you 🫶🏽🥹💖✨

INSPIRED 🥹
READY FOR NEXT YEAR. NEW MUSIC. NEW GOALS ✨
THANK YOU TO EVERYONE WHO’S LISTENED 🫶🏽
“ So, what do you do for fun ? “ ☺️😂
2023; Thank you for all of the blessings & your lessons 🥂✨
